name: Zone 2 with 30sec Spiked Tempo #1
description:
Long Steady Tempo efforts on their own are practical training. But by incorporating 30-second high-intensity efforts into them, you will improve your body's ability to work aerobically for long periods. 



Today's sessions consist of a 12-minute Tempo effort with a 30-second surge every 3.5 minutes.
